snippet.title: Music Download Center
snippet.description: Music Download Center is a Software that helps you find and download music, browse the internet and listen to many web radios.

snippet.title: Midi Sheet Music
snippet.description: Midi Sheet Music is a free program that plays MIDI music files while highlighting the piano notes and sheet music notes. Works on Windows, Mac OS X, and Ubuntu Linux.

snippet.title: Pure Data Computer Music System
snippet.description: The Pure Data (short Pd) project on SourceForge unifies the extensions (or externals) written for the Pure Data Graphical Computer Music System written by Miller Puckette with contributions from many others.

snippet.title: OBS music stream displayer
snippet.description: Outputs your current playing music to a .txt

snippet.title: MusicStaves
snippet.description: A toolkit for experimenting with different methods for staff removal from digital images of sheet music. This toolkit is based on and requires the Gamera document image analysis framework (http://gamera.sf.net)

snippet.title: Guayadeque Music Player
snippet.description: Guayadeque is a music management program designed for all music enthusiasts. It is Full Featured Linux media player that can easily manage large collections and uses the Gstreamer media framework. More information? http://guayadeque.org
